description: Demolition of the former NHS Trust Site and erection of a three storey building with set back fourth floor providing 49 new homes, comprising 17 x 1 bed, 22 x 2 bed and 10 x 3 bed, proposed basement accommodating 30 car parking spaces, 84 cycle parking spaces and landscaping at ground floor.
